    <item>
      <title>伊朗指责西方对核武器的担忧“具有误导性”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/iran-accuses-west-of-misleading-concerns-over-nuclear-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗指责德国、法国和英国威胁可能撤销 2015 年核协议中给予的一些制裁救济，导致紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/iran-accuses-west-of-misleading-concerns-over-nuclear-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登向情人承认自己是个“酒鬼和瘾君子”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hunter-biden-admitted-to-lover-he-was-a-drunk-and-an-addict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登的前情人在枪支审判期间作证说，她经常恳求他去接受可卡因和酒精成瘾治疗，但他一直“像孩子一样逃跑”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hunter-biden-admitted-to-lover-he-was-a-drunk-and-an-addict</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·班农因藐视法庭罪被勒令 7 月入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bannon-ordered-to-jail-by-july-as-he-fights-contempt-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[史蒂夫·班农是前总统唐纳德·特朗普的长期顾问，他上诉推翻 2022 年藐视国会的判决失败，因此被勒令在 7 月 1 日前开始服刑四个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bannon-ordered-to-jail-by-july-as-he-fights-contempt-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员蒂姆·斯科特将花费 1400 万美元为特朗普争取黑人选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/senator-tim-scott-to-spend-14-million-wooing-black-voters-for-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南卡罗来纳州参议员蒂姆·斯科特是唐纳德·特朗普竞选搭档的头号候选人，他正在进行公开巡回演讲，向他的潜在老板展示他能为共和党总统候选人带来什么：黑人选民和亿万富翁捐助者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/senator-tim-scott-to-spend-14-million-wooing-black-voters-for-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登排除赦免儿子亨特的可能性并将尊重判决结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-rules-out-pardon-for-son-hunter-will-respect-verdict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，如果他的儿子亨特因联邦刑事指控被判有罪，他将排除赦免的可能性，并将尊重判决。拜登在谈到可能影响他与唐纳德·特朗普竞选连任的法律案件时表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-rules-out-pardon-for-son-hunter-will-respect-verdict</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朱利安·哈里斯和阿莱格拉·斯特拉顿：财富与税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-06/julian-harris-and-allegra-stratton-wealth-and-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大家好，欢迎收看《The Readout》。在 7 月 4 日大选之前，《The Readout》将由 Allegra Stratton 和 Ailbhe Rea 以及新闻编辑室的其他同事共同撰写，在竞选活动展开时为您提供额外的视角和分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-06/julian-harris-and-allegra-stratton-wealth-and-taxes</guid>
